        "subject": "LU-645 llite: Avoid unnecessary dentry rehashing",
        "message": "LU-645 llite: Avoid unnecessary dentry rehashing\n\nIn patchless case the sequence __d_drop() then d_rehash_cond() creates\nrace window if dentry is already hashed, in this case rehashing should\nbe avoided.\n\nSigned-off-by: Bobi Jam <bobijam@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Ie63071f87bb12b674529d119443935c826bf7445\n"
